Rating: 4
I'm not so comfortable on the grill, and always kind of had doubts about bbq'ing corn (mostly b/c its so good already). This recipe is delicious, and tastes like a fun salad on the cob. I grilled the corn a little more after I put the pesto on, made the garlic roast a little. Nice touch.

